As a player,
So I can enjoy a game of bowling,
I want to follow the traditional rules of bowling.

As a player,
So I can enjoy a game of bowling,
I want two opportunities per frame to knock down ten pins.

As a player,
So I can enjoy a game of bowling,
I want the frame to end when I get a strike.

As a player,
So I can know how I am doing in my bowling game,
I want to see my running score.

As a player,
So I can know how I am doing in my bowling game,
I want bonus points for my strikes and spares.
